snippet.title: Yes, Your Grace: Snowfall - World Premiere Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam ➟ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1373090/

Yes, Your Grace: Snowfall is a cinematic kingdom management game. Make alliances, support your loved ones and fight for your home. Challenge your petitioner's intent and decide if you want to satisfy their pleas!

A huge thank you to Artur Dzivia for supplying music for the trailer: https://www.youtube.com/@Dzivia

Game Developed & Published by Brave At Night.
#SummerGameFest #worldpremiere #yesyourgrace
